{"tid":897793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食麻辣派對送安全套","createTime":"2018-11-11T08:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T08:34:03.000Z","uid":201795,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c09c76fe1f4cf2127a07b5e8311a68eb09a75423","tid":897793,"uid":201795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"上次去銅鑼灣間麻辣派對幫襯<br />\n埋單時前面個大陸客哥哥仔問左句<br />\n「可以給我一些方便套嗎？」<br />\n當陣時我就頭都大埋心諗佢想要尿壼定dumdum<br />\n邊有得咁樣問staff攞<br />\n點知又真係乜都冇講放左啲dumdum入佢手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大陸哥哥出去搵女主角仲比人鬧<br />\n「三個怎麼夠用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n有冇巴絲打去餐廳吃野都攞過<br />\n利申未有女伴，日日屋企打飛機<br />\n費事浪費人地店鋪資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTrQg18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTrQg18.png&h=92e22a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSrXGt2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSrXGt2.png&h=39d5a234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12591bc20dc36f0802def4e6d0388a09fb81ec20","tid":897793,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"TB不了"},{"pid":"fff3a0972b82f06bff24160e73fd818175c00c7f","tid":897793,"uid":201795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"12591bc20dc36f0802def4e6d0388a09fb81ec20","tid":897793,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"TB不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCVmoNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCVmoNx.png&h=a6c971b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNVEUUd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2